name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania v. Roger Seamon PROCTOR, Appellant

judges: Before NIX, C.J., and LARSEN, FLAHERTY, McDERMOTT, ZAPPALA, PAPADAKOS and STOUT, JJ.
parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania v. Roger Seamon PROCTOR, Appellant.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM:
Matter remanded to Court of Common Pleas of Crawford County for a suppression hearing to determine the legality of appellant’s arrest in the State of Ohio and the admissibility of statements and other evidence obtained as a result of that detention.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM:
